stories.text: This question is open to all genders and so on. I'm just curious if there are situations in which you had a rockstar glow because of your contributions to a major open source project. I mean, bravo if that has happened to you; I personally am in favor of such things. It might be motivational for you to share!
stories.title: Ask HN: Does committer status on a major project get you laid?

stories.text:
We're all remote and planning to have a social hour once a week or once every two weeks. Previously we did a life review where people had to walk through some of the events in the life. This was fun.

Any other ideas? No, we are not allowed to spend money on this. Themes/ideas for a recurring social hour would be great. Thanks.
